1
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:26,700
Jingzhi.

2
00:00:28,260 --> 00:00:29,520
You are in the capital,

3
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,530
you must be suffering more than me.

4
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:57,630
Commander.

5
00:00:58,430 --> 00:00:59,100
The grain,

6
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:03,430
The grain personally supervised by the Imperial Noble Consort

7
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,860
is thirty miles away.

8
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,060
Great victory, Commander!

9
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,560
100,000 piculs of military rations sent from the capital

10
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,030
are already 30 miles away.

11
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:02,530
Liu Yong, the Minister of Revenue, secretly withheld the rations,

12
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:05,130
so the Emperor executed his nine generations.

13
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,330
It's her.

14
00:02:10,229 --> 00:02:12,660
In that ruthless, man-eating palace,

15
00:02:13,230 --> 00:02:16,160
she forced open a path to greatness for me.

16
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,660
All troops, listen to my command.

17
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:25,630
Follow me to flatten the Yu army's camp tonight.

18
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,960
We will use the enemies' heads

19
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,000
as a sacrifice to our flag.

20
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,700
Kill!

21
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,130
Kill!

22
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:34,230
Kill!

23
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:56,560
Sister Qu being promoted to Imperial Noble Consort

24
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,329
is truly a miracle in the harem.

25
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,860
I specifically ordered someone to brew this

26
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:09,730
Safflower and Snow Lotus Soup for you, Sister,

27
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,700
wishing you to bear children for the Emperor soon.

28
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:23,320
Imperial Noble Consort, this is a favor from Her Majesty the Empress.

29
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:30,520
A lowly servant from the Yeting Bureau like you,

30
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,500
kneel and thank her for the favor

31
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:33,960
and drink the soup.

32
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,329
Safflower and Snow Lotus Soup.

33
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,260
Consort Li, you must be mistaken.

34
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,430
This is clearly a deadly soup with three mace of heartbreak grass

35
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:42,500
and five mace of oleander.

36
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:48,790
Since you like this favor so much, Your Highness,

37
00:03:48,930 --> 00:03:50,960
why don't you drink it yourself?

38
00:03:51,730 --> 00:03:52,530
Insolent!

39
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,030
You lowly servant,

40
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,760
how dare you slander the Empress!

41
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,560
Someone,

42
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,329
hold her down

43
00:03:58,329 --> 00:03:59,930
and force it down her throat.

44
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,060
Qu Jingzhi, are you rebelling?

45
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,330
What are you doing?

46
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:10,530
What am I doing?

47
00:04:10,730 --> 00:04:12,830
I swore on the first day I entered the palace

48
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,030
that whoever dares to take my life,

49
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,560
I will slaughter their entire family!

50
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,560
Let go of me! Drink it!

51
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:19,630
You ruthless idiots,

52
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:20,860
do you really think I, Qu Jingzhi,

53
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:22,920
am still a piece of meat at your mercy?

54
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:11,760
Jingzhi, I love it when you look like this.

55
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:14,400
It's about time this harem saw some blood.

56
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:15,700
Pass on my decree:

57
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,860
Consort Li attempted to murder the Imperial Noble Consort,

58
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:18,930
she deserves to die.

59
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:20,460
The Empress failed to manage her subordinates and is grounded.

60
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:24,660
All affairs of the six palaces are entrusted to the Imperial Noble Consort.

61
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:32,860
Long live Your Highness!
